Objective: Calculate the total number of study days remaining from the current date until the specified exam date. Use the generate_and_execute_code tool to perform an accurate date calculation using Python.

Output Format: Provide the total number of remaining days as a single numeric value. Use the system_objective_fulfilled tool to report the final result.

User Input / Context: exam_date: {{"type":"in","path":"ask_user_exam_date","title":"Exam Date"}}

Objective: Create a comprehensive and personalized study plan for the exam {{"type":"in","path":"ask_user_exam_name","title":"Exam Name"}} scheduled on {{"type":"in","path":"ask_user_exam_date","title":"Exam Date"}}. The plan must cover a total duration of {{"type":"in","path":"node_step_calculated_total_number_of_study_days","title":"Calculate Total Study Days"}} days with a daily commitment of {{"type":"in","path":"ask_user_daily_study_hours","title":"Daily Study Hours"}} hours. Distribute study time across the following subjects: {{"type":"in","path":"ask_user_subjects","title":"Subjects"}}, ensuring heavy emphasis and more time allocation for the specified weak areas: {{"type":"in","path":"ask_user_weak_areas","title":"Weak Areas"}}. The plan should follow the user's preferred style: {{"type":"in","path":"ask_user_plan_type_preference","title":"Plan Type Preference"}} and incorporate any additional requirements provided: {{"type":"in","path":"ask_user_user_input","title":"User Input"}}.

Output Format: Provide the complete textual content of the study plan. Ensure the schedule is logically sequenced and realistic given the daily hour limit. Once the content is generated, use system_objective_fulfilled to complete the task.

User Input / Context:
Exam Name: {{"type":"in","path":"ask_user_exam_name","title":"Exam Name"}}
Exam Date: {{"type":"in","path":"ask_user_exam_date","title":"Exam Date"}}
Total Study Days: {{"type":"in","path":"node_step_calculated_total_number_of_study_days","title":"Calculate Total Study Days"}}
Daily Study Hours: {{"type":"in","path":"ask_user_daily_study_hours","title":"Daily Study Hours"}}
Subjects: {{"type":"in","path":"ask_user_subjects","title":"Subjects"}}
Weak Areas: {{"type":"in","path":"ask_user_weak_areas","title":"Weak Areas"}}
Plan Type Preference: {{"type":"in","path":"ask_user_plan_type_preference","title":"Plan Type Preference"}}
Additional Context: {{"type":"in","path":"ask_user_user_input","title":"User Input"}}
